{"tid":44091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇尋麻疹既人","createTime":"2016-12-18T04:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T10:02:59.000Z","uid":49258,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aebcae8f23c6e09ea206101947b05ae0959834b6","tid":44091,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:01:32.000Z","msg":"呢種天氣，時凍時熱，一出太陽係街到行陣就成個人都紅扑扑又痕，好想斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76862185a55c9ce21d9db175caf04f31f098ac56","tid":44091,"uid":55635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:10:34.000Z","msg":"細個嚴重d ,無啦啦都可以有，  <br />\n而家就係通常轉天氣或者俾野壓到有痕先有"},{"pid":"9e34aa404fa8240a7c24158ee120006ffe3bdffe","tid":44091,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:12:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dadf3913536f0f8c723bce341d3397d110ad019e","tid":44091,"uid":36953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:15:28.000Z","msg":"我有 已經三年 斷唔到尾"},{"pid":"fd0c21f122da4be2fb3d1cf42b6a00714ddf3204","tid":44091,"uid":3506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:29:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個嚴重d ,無啦啦都可以有，  <br />\n而家就係通常轉天氣或者俾野壓到有痕先有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係 好似叫皮膚劃痕症"},{"pid":"032f7332645d347febb0f8248f8bc58abd61af7e","tid":44091,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:34:23.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n以前要喺toilet哩個幾兩個鍾<br />\n而家日日食藥<br />\n除咗好眼訓 都無乜大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n的確好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5326f6f2b965d86eb4b376f357d168ecc7a5e1cd","tid":44091,"uid":60313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:36:01.000Z","msg":"已經5年<br />\n5年前去左日本箱根浸溫泉, 返黎就開始有, 懷疑浸得太盡導致皮膚表層保護油脂無左, 曾經睇過一個出名中醫食左1星期就好返, 之後貪食無戒口就現返形, 呢家一返屋企就會想R痕, 可以身上寫字寄愛意<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9ad551a53c792d04745934bb45d45854dcf2ad","tid":44091,"uid":52357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:37:54.000Z","msg":"細個試過有 睇完中醫又搽藥膏又食藥 好似係啲中藥粉溝熱水就得 呀媽又唔知煲左啲咩比我浸腳 係就唔痕好翻 但啲疤痕呀印呀仲係到 7年都未退"},{"pid":"291a00e4139fedd328cdf5e963bfd03b18f6d636","tid":44091,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:49:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<br />\n以前要喺toilet哩個幾兩個鍾<br />\n而家日日食藥<br />\n除咗好眼訓 都無乜大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n的確好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都有食藥，不過聽人講食得多會無效所以忍住隔一排先會食，唔敢日日都食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f851b4a2e79169d75311917bfb2087e6c1b6a2","tid":44091,"uid":1110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:51:53.000Z","msg":"早兩年發過， 唔食得海鮮<br />\n睇左半年中醫先醫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10416bdfa60e068ce67b2dbd5ce0de40e830119","tid":44091,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪好似風懶？</blockquote><br />\n類似，但我都唔太清楚分到兩樣<br />\n只係知自己症狀係尋麻疹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79fc29c48be30ebde07481283f698a9a7e1da01","tid":44091,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:53:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個嚴重d ,無啦啦都可以有，  <br />\n而家就係通常轉天氣或者俾野壓到有痕先有</blockquote><br />\n唔轉天氣都一直出，真係頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf751fc6cf35292bd64136814f4372ced73af8f2","tid":44091,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早兩年發過， 唔食得海鮮<br />\n睇左半年中醫先醫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我少食海鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能無乜關係，介口就真係有必要"},{"pid":"c2e7c5b921601cfe1be668418621398f47281fab","tid":44091,"uid":31941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:56:45.000Z","msg":"一熱就出點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29bcbb62c9393f7d96361903937a4387c1674550","tid":44091,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:58:12.000Z","msg":"一有敏感野就起爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d29d1bff9eee9b579ddeeb3c15a263251f48f89a","tid":44091,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:59:38.000Z","msg":"春袋有 好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd62e32ef7b89f0a8db3bda200bbf801d571428","tid":44091,"uid":47469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:06:50.000Z","msg":"前幾年轉季有 生到全身都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搽藥膏 搽佐半年 宜家間唔中都有一兩點"},{"pid":"10fb5903e4092329b729576a60682797bf44e565","tid":44091,"uid":43979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T17:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3796faf8d40c20f22df3faa5203b71743a36503","tid":44091,"uid":43979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:02:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}